                Built with love in India 🇮🇳, our platform ensures security, speed, and convenience for everyone.
            </p>
            <p>
                Backed by <b>YTP & Company Pvt Ltd</b>, we are continuously improving and expanding
                our services to make billing smarter and more reliable.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
